{"tid":1786954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港共產化? 郭文貴50億香港豪宅 戶口被充公","createTime":"2019-12-17T14:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T08:49:55.000Z","uid":165683,"like":196,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca19694b0377707efb2dde3215011ae5c3537dc","tid":1786954,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:11:38.000Z","msg":"香港仲有無私有產權? 你話就收?<br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的「紅色富豪」郭文貴 ，曾經大爆中共醜聞， 兩年多前已經警告香港人，大爆國安、公安經常跨境在港執法。重看過去半年逆權運動，這位與共產黨交手的紅色富豪果然「先知先覺」。<br />\n<br />\n君不見警務處處長鄧炳强，一上任就上京「朝聖」，在天安門看著國旗「感動」一番，還口口聲聲感謝公安支持支持，語氣十足跟老細稟報一樣。不過近年郭文貴已靜下來，事關無水自然沒咁好唱口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_714148_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_714148_0&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0le0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=8d340e31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_714148_0&h=5082fa02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_714148_0</a>"},{"pid":"52a1ebecd4b0517f3c9d849f088d0ae80e18d804","tid":1786954,"uid":293951,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"已充公？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed29a44d3ee8340f768a22ccd55d9728b57a146b","tid":1786954,"uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"52a1ebecd4b0517f3c9d849f088d0ae80e18d804","tid":1786954,"uid":293951,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"已充公？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:13:42.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"1d5276d35c1b68235f05039575c20325166fd546","tid":1786954,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a785900a415e112b42f8e0020b2aef1982e1be93","tid":1786954,"uid":343361,"like":10,"dislike":12,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:14